snippet.title: Dual Destiny in Pokémon GO - A new Season is here!
snippet.description:
Trainers, this upcoming Season will have you GO-ing! 

Dual Destiny is bringing #PokemonGOTour: Unova, Paldea Pokémon debuts, and more new adventures to #PokemonGO!

December 3 at 10:00 a.m. – March 4 at 10:00 a.m. local time

https://pokemongolive.com/seasons/dual-destiny
